# Java TestNG Foundation

Automation learning project using Java, Maven, and TestNG.

## Tech Stack

- Java 17
- Maven
- TestNG
- Git
- GitHub

## What this project includes

- Basic assertion tests
- TestNG suite execution
- `@BeforeMethod` and `@AfterMethod` usage
- Clean test naming
- Simple project structure

